age does not exist)\">Haiying Wang</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Noah_Weninger&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Noah Weninger (page does not exist)\">Noah Weninger</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Fan_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Fan Yang (page does not exist)\">Fan Yang</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Zhonghua_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Zhonghua Yang (page does not exist)\">Zhonghua Yang</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chun_Ye\" title=\"Chun Ye\">Chun Ye</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ling_Zhao&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ling Zhao (page does not exist)\">Ling Zhao</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Internet_Collegiate_Chess_League\">Internet Collegiate Chess League</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Alberta&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Internet Collegiate Chess League\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Internet Collegiate Chess League Team Champions 1998-9 with perfect score (4/4) <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>&#160;:\n</p>\n<ul><li> Board 1: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/perl/chessplayer?pid=110850\">David Ottosen</a></li>\n<li> Board 2: <a href=\"/Yngvi_Bj%C3%B6rnsson\" title=\"Yngvi Björnsson\">Yngvi Björnsson</a></li>\n<li> Board 3: Dmitri Shefer</li>\n<li> Board 4: <a href=\"/Adrien_Regimbald\" title=\"Adrien Regimbald\">Adrien Regimbald</a></li>\n<li> Alternate: Aaron Levi</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Alberta&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/WCCC_1989\" title=\"WCCC 1989\">WCCC 1989</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Alberta&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/%7Esmillie/\">Keith Smillie</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i>The Department of Computing Science: The First Twenty-Five Years</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://webdocs.cs.ualberta.ca/%7Esmillie/DeptHist/TR9101.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jonathan_Schaeffer\" title=\"Jonathan Schaeffer\">Jonathan Schaeffer</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i>The GAMES group at the University of Alberta</i>. <a href=\"/5th_Computer_Olympiad#Workshop\" title=\"5th Computer Olympiad\">5th Computer Olympiad Workshop</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=University_of_Alberta&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Alberta\">University of Alberta from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ualberta.ca/\">University of Alberta</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.ualberta.ca/computing-science/\">Department of Computing Science</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http